headline: Super Micro Computer (NasdaqGS:SMCI) Partners With US Data Centers For Alabama Expansion
summary: Super Micro Computer (NasdaqGS:SMCI) saw an impressive 41% increase in share price over the past month, partly driven by its collaboration with Digi Power X and US Data Centers, aiming to expand data center operations with B200 GPU racks. Further fueling investor interest, Super Micro inked a partnership with DataVolt to explore AI infrastructure in Saudi Arabia. Meanwhile, the market saw slight gains, with major indices like the Nasdaq increasing modestly. Despite these broader market...
